						<h2><a href="http://www.nutsvolts.com/magazine/article/signal-generators-part-1" style="color:#333">Signal Generators &#8212; Part 1</a></h2>
						<p><p>Signal generators are devices used to make the signals used in testing and troubleshooting of radio receivers and other circuits, so are of primary interest to almost everyone interested in electronics.</p></p>
					</div>
					
