					</div>
					<div class="col-md-5">
						<h6 class="tags">Data Acquisition</h6>
						<h2><a href="http://www.nutsvolts.com/magazine/article/march2013_newton" style="color:#333">A Recording Radiation Counter</a></h2>
						<p><p>Are you exposed? Build this unit to detect and display levels of radiation, plus you can record months of data to keep track of just how toxic areas may be or become.</p></p>
