						<h2><a href="http://www.nutsvolts.com/magazine/article/july2012_Guyer" style="color:#333">Build the Solar Sequencer</a></h2>
						<p><p>Build a solar sequencer that enables a single solar panel to charge multiple batteries of different sizes and capacities, keeping them isolated from each other.</p></p>
